trans-unit.source: To use RapidStart Services tables and pages are created, but there is no data in them.

target.mrk: Pro použití služeb RapidStart jsou vytvořeny tabulky a stránky, ale v nich nejsou žádná data.

trans-unit.source: To use RapidStart Services for [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], you first create a new company for which you want to perform a customer implementation.

seg-source.mrk: To use RapidStart Services for [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], you first create a new company for which you want to perform a customer implementation.

target.mrk: Chcete-li používat služby RapidStart pro [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], musíte nejprve vytvořit novou společnost, pro kterou chcete provést implementaci zákazníka.

trans-unit.source: When you create a new company, the standard [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] tables and pages are created, but there is no data in them.

seg-source.mrk: When you create a new company, the standard [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] tables and pages are created, but there is no data in them.

target.mrk: Když vytvoříte novou společnost, vytvoří se standardní tabulky a stránky [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], ale v nich nejsou žádná data.

trans-unit.source: In addition, you can apply specific setup data to your company after you initialize it.

seg-source.mrk: In addition, you can apply specific setup data to your company after you initialize it.

target.mrk: Kromě toho můžete po inicializaci použít ve vaší společnosti konkrétní instalační data.

trans-unit.source: The information is provided in a configuration package, a .rapidstart file, which delivers content in a compressed format.

seg-source.mrk: The information is provided in a configuration package, a .rapidstart file, which delivers content in a compressed format.

target.mrk: Informace jsou poskytovány v konfiguračním balíčku, souboru .rapidstart, který dodává obsah v komprimovaném formátu.

trans-unit.source: Example configuration packages, including country/region-specific files, are included with the CRONUS demonstration company.

seg-source.mrk: Example configuration packages, including country/region-specific files, are included with the CRONUS demonstration company.

target.mrk: Příklady konfiguračních balíčků, včetně souborů specifických pro zemi nebo oblast, jsou součástí demonstrační společnosti CRONUS.

trans-unit.source: Use the following procedures to use the example configuration package with a new company.

seg-source.mrk: Use the following procedures to use the example configuration package with a new company.

target.mrk: Použijte následující postupy pro použití vzorového konfiguračního balíčku s novou společností.

trans-unit.source: To use the sample BASICCONFIG configuration package

seg-source.mrk: To use the sample BASICCONFIG configuration package

trans-unit.source: Open the CRONUS International Ltd. company.

seg-source.mrk: Open the CRONUS International Ltd. company.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Changing Basic Settings](ui-change-basic-settings.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Changing Basic Settings](ui-change-basic-settings.md).

target.mrk: Pro další informace se podívejte na [Změna základního nastavení](ui-change-basic-settings.md).

trans-unit.source: Choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Configuration Packages**, and then choose the related link.

seg-source.mrk: Choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Configuration Packages**, and then choose the related link.

target.mrk: Vyberte ikonu ![Žárovka, která otevře funkci Řekněte mi](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Řekněte mi, co chcete dělat"), zvolte **Konfigurační balíčky** a poté vyberte související odkaz.

trans-unit.source: Choose the BASICCONFIG package from the list, and then choose the **Export Package** action.

seg-source.mrk: Choose the BASICCONFIG package from the list, and then choose the **Export Package** action.

target.mrk: Vyberte balíček BASICCINFOG ze seznamu a poté vyberte akci **Exportovat balíček**.

trans-unit.source: Use the following procedure to create a new company, and use the BASICCONFIG package as part of the process.

seg-source.mrk: Use the following procedure to create a new company, and use the BASICCONFIG package as part of the process.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Creating New Companies in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)]](about-new-company.md).

trans-unit.source: From the RapidStart Services Implementer Role Center, you can now import the configuration package that you exported from the CRONUS International Ltd. company.

target.mrk: Z role Implementátor služeb RapidStart můžete nyní importovat konfigurační balíček, který jste exportovali od společnosti CRONUS International Ltd.

trans-unit.source: After you create a new company, some tables are automatically filled in, even if no company template is applied.
